  "item": [
    {
      "name": "06. Order",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Buyer",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "[POST] Checkout 🔒",
              "request": {
                "auth": {
                  "type": "bearer",
                  "bearer": [
                    {
                      "key": "token",
                      "value": "{{access_token}}",
                      "type": "string"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "X-Idempotency-Key",
                    "value": "{{idempotency_key}}"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/orders/checkout",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "orders",
                    "checkout"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Buat order dari cart items. Satu entri `items[]` = satu toko = satu Order.\n\n**`item_ids` (optional):** Array ID cart_item spesifik yang ingin di-checkout dari toko ini. Jika tidak disertakan / null → semua item dari toko tersebut di-checkout sekaligus.\n\n**Contoh partial checkout** (3 item di toko, hanya checkout item ke-3):\n```json\n{ \"store_id\": 1, \"item_ids\": [42] }\n```\n\nItem yang tidak di-checkout **tetap di cart** (tidak dihapus).\n\n**Selalu sertakan `X-Idempotency-Key`** header (UUID) untuk mencegah double order.\n\n`shipping_fee` diterima as-is (Sprint 8 akan tambah re-validasi backend via ShippingService).",
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"store_id\": \"{{store_id}}\",\n      \"address_id\": \"{{address_id}}\",\n      \"shipping_courier\": \"jne\",\n      \"shipping_service\": \"REG\",\n      \"shipping_fee\": 1500000,\n      \"notes\": \"Tolong bubble wrap\",\n      \"item_ids\": null  // optional: specific cart_item IDs — omit to checkout ALL items from store\n    }\n  ],\n  \"voucher_code\": null\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                }
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "201 Created — Full checkout",
                  "status": "Created",
                  "code": 201,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Checkout successful.\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"order_number\": \"INV/2026/05/000001\",\n      \"status\": \"pending\",\n      \"total_cents\": 39000000,\n      \"total\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n      \"items\": [\n        {\n          \"product_name\": \"Sepatu Lari\",\n          \"quantity\": 1,\n          \"unit_price_cents\": 39000000\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "201 Created — Partial checkout (item_ids)",
                  "status": "Created",
                  "code": 201,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Checkout successful.\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"order_number\": \"INV/2026/05/000002\",\n      \"status\": \"pending\",\n      \"total_cents\": 15000000,\n      \"total\": \"Rp 150.000\",\n      \"items\": [\n        {\n          \"product_name\": \"Kaos Polos Hitam\",\n          \"quantity\": 1,\n          \"unit_price_cents\": 15000000\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:01:00.000000Z\"\n  }\n}"
                }
              ],
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test(\"Status 201\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                      "pm.test(\"Has order data\", () => {",
                      "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                      "    pm.expect(j.data).to.be.an(\"array\");",
                      "    if (j.data && j.data[0]) {",
                      "        pm.collectionVariables.set(\"order_id\", j.data[0].id);",
                      "    }",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "[GET] List My Orders 🔒",
              "request": {
                "auth": {
                  "type": "bearer",
                  "bearer": [
                    {
                      "key": "token",
                      "value": "{{access_token}}",
                      "type": "string"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/orders",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "orders"
                  ],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "status",
                      "value": "",
                      "description": "Filter: pending|paid|processing|shipped|delivered|completed|cancelled|disputed",
                      "disabled": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "description": "List all orders for authenticated buyer. Optional ?status= filter."
              },
              "response": [],
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                      "pm.test(\"Has pagination\", () => {",
                      "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                      "    pm.expect(j.meta).to.have.property(\"pagination\");",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "[GET] Get Order Detail 🔒",
              "request": {
                "auth": {
                  "type": "bearer",
                  "bearer": [
                    {
                      "key": "token",
                      "value": "{{access_token}}",
                      "type": "string"
